<div class="shortcode-info">
    <p>Use the shortcode <i style="background: #dedede; padding: 4px;">[aikezi_info]</i> to display all the information below. If you want custom display use the shortcode <i style="background: #dedede; padding: 4px;">[aikezi_info id="info id"]</i> with comma separated info id.
    To display the image, use the shortcode: <i style="background: #dedede; padding: 4px;">[aikezi_info_photo]</i> </p>
</div>